{"type": "article", "id": 12171, "title": "Nendo 香蕉标签", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-16T10:29:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185149cmpySiOEHQ9zKoks.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tNendo 最近为日本的 Unifrutti 公司设计了一款非常有趣的香蕉标签，标签的样子和香蕉表皮一样，而撕开一层，会看到香蕉的简介，再撕下去，才是真正的香蕉表皮。此外，香蕉的手提袋完全展开后是一张完整的“大蕉叶”。这款香蕉被叫做 “幸福香蕉”，是一款来自菲律宾棉兰岛的有机香蕉，曾经以口味和品质赢得过比利时顶级美味大赛的冠军。这款香蕉仅仅在日本发售，不过对我们本土的设计师来说，把标签做的这么好玩，也是不错的启发吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140005kbnrAh8OW2EV1vTR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140005pbtQOJeXHYN7w4RW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140006Er7CDPJdNwLhmtnM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140006Tx2U0sY9gCpZmqu3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400079McE4Ya3Wx2THk0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}